Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Prepare and season the chicken and onion.', '2. Preheat the oven to the desired temperature.', 
'3. Place the chicken and onion in the oven and roast.']

behavior prepare_and_season(chicken:item, onion:item):
    body:
        # Ensure both chicken and onion are cleaned
        wash(chicken)
        wash(onion)

        # Cut the onion after cleaning
        achieve cut(onion)

        # Once washed, season the chicken
        scrub(chicken)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken)
        # Select the chicken to be prepared and seasoned

        bind onion: item where:
            is_food_onion(onion)
        # Select the onion to be prepared and seasoned

        prepare_and_season(chicken, onion)

Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Prepare the chicken and onion for roasting.', '2. Roast the chicken with the onion in the oven.
']

behavior clean_food(item:item, sink:item, faucet:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(item, sink)
        if is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink):
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            wash(item)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)
        else:
            wash(item)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken)
        bind onion: item where:
            is_food_onion(onion)
        bind sink: item where:
            is_sink(sink)
        bind faucet: item where:
            is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
        clean_food(chicken, sink, faucet)
        clean_food(onion, sink, faucet)

def in_oven(chicken:item, onion:item, oven:item):
    # Function to check if chicken and onion are both inside the oven
    symbol both_in_oven=inside(chicken, oven) and inside(onion, oven)
    return both_in_oven

behavior prepare_oven(chicken:item, onion:item, oven:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(chicken, oven) # Place chicken inside the oven
        achieve inside(onion, oven) # Place onion inside the oven

behavior start_roasting(oven:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(oven) # Ensure the oven is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken)
        # Select the chicken to roast
        
        bind onion: item where:
            is_food_onion(onion)
        # Select the onion to roast
        
        bind oven: item where:
            is_oven(oven)
        # Select an oven
        
        if not in_oven(chicken, onion, oven):
            prepare_oven(chicken, onion, oven)
        start_roasting(oven) # Start the roasting process
